						<summary>

						<p>This registers a provision made for the daily supply of a <hi rend="italic">kuṟuṇi</hi> and <hi rend="italic">nāḻi</hi> of paddy for the <hi rend="italic">tiruchchennaḍai</hi> service in the (Vishnu) temple of Tirumēṟṟaḷi-Nakkar at Malaiyamāṉ-Aṟṟūr, a <hi rend="italic">brahmadēya</hi> in Aṟṟūr-kūṟṟam a sub-division of Milāḍu, by <hi rend="bold">Ninnāvaḍutuṟaiyaṉ</hi> and two other persons who are stated to be the <hi rend="bold">collectors of tolls in Milāḍu, Vāṇagappāḍi and Ōram</hi> (?) divisions. </p>						

						</summary>
